</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B1406002001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Open air cleaner case (1) by unhooking its clamps (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141018.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "57.642mm" ver = "01" gw = "199" gh = "147"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove air cleaner filter from case.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B1406002002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B1406003">Air Cleaner Filter Inspection and Cleaning</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure.
</ptxt>
